author: cmpilato
msg: Merging work from /branches/issue-745-dev into /trunk.  For the
details of this merge, see the following revisions:
No tweaks were needed to make this merge work.
**IMPORTANT**  This set of changes makes Subversion unable to work
with repositories created using older versions of Subversion.  You
must use a previous version of Subversion to `svnadmin dump' your
existing repositories, then use this version (or later) to `svnadmin
create; svnadmin load' them again.
